      "full_name": "Joint Stock Company Scientific and Production Enterprise “Military Technologies”",
      "is_primary": true
    }
  ],
  "remarks": "JSC Scientific and Production Enterprise “Military Technologies” is a Russian defence enterprise that develops and manufactures high-tech and high-quality complex military-technical equipment, automated control systems and open-source software and decision support systems. The company, on the orders of the Russian Ministry of Defence, has developed the 1A50 Komandor-VT tablet artillery system, which was presented at the Army-2023 military technical forum. For that development, JSC Scientific and Production Enterprise “Military Technologies” used experience gained by its hardware and software being implemented in the frontline of Russia’s war of aggression against Ukraine. In 2024, a batch of its portable tablets designed for preparation and control of artillery fire was sent to an artillery unit for testing in combat conditions.",
  "@context": "https://www.ammitto.org/ontology/context.jsonld"
}